        <h3>Check your DMARC right now</h3>
        <p>Run a free DNSSnuff report to see your current DMARC policy, whether it's correctly formatted, and what to fix.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Run Free Report →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
